<taxonomicName id="37C69096B2550A99F3D168ED2799C256" authority="Gilomen" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Carex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="427" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rosae">
Carex 
<normalizedToken id="FF373A6F8B8203ACD2F8FD222CEC16E8" originalValue="Rósae" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Rosae</normalizedToken>
Gilomen
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="E27BD82E880490D4C0F98941656A0EBE" pageId="null" pageNumber="427" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="B0E1F45C3ADCD88EC986B2C6ED18A204" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Rosa-Segge</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="38837D0C089BB5FC3AA933BBB9B6ABA8" pageId="null" pageNumber="427" type="description">
<paragraph id="1FA356C1F0E009F6DA6D12A9FFCB20F4" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">
Habitus wie 
<taxonomicName id="535DF731B3B9D8B764FE9A83330338A8" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Carex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="427" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="curvula">
<emphasis id="57CC31B9341A35FBF812B8951CC0AC6C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">C. curvula</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 11). 
<normalizedToken id="6116F9C225E2C55E1FA464CB44E2079A" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
1-2 mm breit, im Querschnitt 
<emphasis id="E00A8159AB2BA150EF473EAC923D86C7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">
sichel- bis 
<normalizedToken id="182CC4B081DECEEFF2A197F8993C6389" originalValue="halbkreisförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">halbkreisfoermig</normalizedToken>
, nur 4mal breiter als dick, ohne Rille 
<normalizedToken id="686A456AC7C9019BC6CFBBC488A28862" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">ueber</normalizedToken>
dem Mittelnerv
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="2ADF72C228A8550EDDCC5F71056F90CE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">mit Mesophyll zwischen Mittelnerv und Epidermis der Blattoberseite</emphasis>
), bald nach der Schneeschmelze im obern Teil absterbend. 
<normalizedToken id="7344FE0A7EE1D1554411D0EC9052A9CB" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="7F0525098CF1FFFD4006A40E403C5F7C" originalValue="Tragblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Tragblaetter</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="5D23CE2F7ABC962D4A08570AB6ECA4A2" originalValue="Fruchtschläuche" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Fruchtschlaeuche</normalizedToken>
wie bei 
<emphasis id="2F432CB52F3A3BAA2B14A4333590690D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">
<taxonomicName id="68A0850E7447C2E9075AFDA6A0DAE451" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Carex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="427" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="curvula">C. curvula</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Narben 3. 
<emphasis id="9AC3944D0F7DBAACB941FD8415185250" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">
<normalizedToken id="B32D0F62A0651DD328B16BD764343F76" originalValue="Staubblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Staubblaetter</normalizedToken>
an der Spitze mit 0,2-0,3 mm langen 
<normalizedToken id="085CA94C216E0A5739A1D94A78B1AAA0" originalValue="Fortsätzen" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Fortsaetzen</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="37D711A25E5ED4A5843CB45121FA3321" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">
<emphasis id="A22B6722904F80C5481B2C6E3FA9415A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="44FBAC109456A6FDF36E2D9B9A9898CA" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">
<emphasis id="CEA2E49CDF5A0DEE26153C24FBD20A9C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Standort.</emphasis>
Wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="09F0A9AE66E2D04F4FEAFF643ACB1010" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Carex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="427" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="curvula">
<emphasis id="2C1024A833B8B8BEE8E0D8340D6CEC45" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">C. curvula</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, jedoch nur auf kalkhaltigem Boden.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="21A49B1E38B29A60C8A3F6035DD2953E" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">
<emphasis id="B393EB875514D13052D7FBE7CAE00C37" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">
Verbreitung. Mittel- 
<normalizedToken id="3F2C9E601F42C14504376D15C1F2FD8E" originalValue="undsüdeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">undsuedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="C886795931BE206F6C28C69A515578E4" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Alpen (Verbreitungszentren in den 
<normalizedToken id="614CD47039AF11E5C576623F6C575237" originalValue="Südwestalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Suedwestalpen</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="395F4B17F3649FF83060FCF2DB104517" originalValue="östlichste" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">oestlichste</normalizedToken>
Fundstelle am 
<normalizedToken id="31EFC5D39697EBF90722011B793A4339" originalValue="Großglockner" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Grossglockner</normalizedToken>
), neuerdings auch aus dem Ljubotengebirge in Mazedonien nachgewiesen (Herbarium Seitter 1957). - Im Gebiet: Ziemlich 
<normalizedToken id="770342E9F15D80C3E59E83BBB8B07006" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">haeufig</normalizedToken>
in Savoyer, Piemonteser, Aostataler, 
<normalizedToken id="76923701960D909DC3DF3940956E2AF1" originalValue="Waadtländer" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Waadtlaender</normalizedToken>
, Walliser und Berner Alpen; selten 
<normalizedToken id="8790D8E40D878B6CF28385604A3832A8" originalValue="östlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">oestlich</normalizedToken>
der Linie 
<normalizedToken id="B6AB2DB1F4A46659DF5D2F731E2E5B70" originalValue="Lötschenpaß-Nufenenpaß" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Loetschenpass-Nufenenpass</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7991352C48BD226847CF331294F58B49" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">
<emphasis id="7CF7280FEC8E9BB3E5AE9AFC244DAE94" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Weitere Angaben 
<normalizedToken id="5CB654769BE06F32B2B75289532B206B" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">ueber</normalizedToken>
Morphologie, 
<normalizedToken id="D8CAC6D219CBD14795DA601ECFB391E6" originalValue="Ökologie" pageId="null" pageNumber="427">Oekologie</normalizedToken>
und Verbreitung bei Gilomen (1938 Gilomen (1941).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
